reviews.text:
Had an Angus steak burrito for lunch here today , mildly spicy. It was quite large and served luke warm. The taste was average and was not too impressed by it.

The restaurant was empty and I was the only customer.  Prices are moderately high. Was not too overwhelmed by the overall standard, it was pretty average.

Staff were quite pleasant.

I love this place. The service is good the food is great. The steak quesadilla is good quality and if you order the big one it's a ton of food. They offer a good drink selection including frozen margaritas. They let you customize your food to your liking. The staff English is good. I will definitely return here next time I'm in Kowloon Bay area.
A quiet and chill night to spend here. Food is really cheap with eatigo discount. Food is ok.
The food is mediocre and expensive. 38hkd for a small coke? Yall trippin
Great burrito, special drinks thats not common in hk
